\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:574:\"<p>WordPress 4.9.4 is now available for download for all earlier WordPress versions. With the publication of release 4.9.3 an error was introduced causing automatic updates to fail. Less than 24 hours later version 4.9.4 was published which contains a fix for said problem. The auto update is fully functional again with version 4.9.4. If you [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-4/\">WordPress 4.9.4 Update Available</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"jab\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3136:\"<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WordPress 4.9.4</a> is now available for download for all earlier WordPress versions. With the publication of release 4.9.3 an error was introduced causing automatic updates to fail. Less than 24 hours later version 4.9.4 was published which contains a fix for said problem. The auto update is fully functional again with version 4.9.4.</p>\n<p>If you have a Managed WordPress website, you have not been affected by this problem. You will automatically be getting the most current version and are not required to do anything yourself.</p>\n<p>As always, <strong>Managed WordPress websites will be updated by 1&amp;1 automatically.</strong> <span id=\"result_box\" class=\"\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"\">In addition, we <span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\">constantly</span> protect your WordPress websites, through technical measures such as firewalls and filters, even before the updates have been implemented.</span></span></p>\n<p>If you have installed WordPress yourself or use a standard installation from the 1&amp;1 App Center, you can update to 4.9.4 from your WordPress <strong>Dashboard.</strong> Select <strong>Updates</strong> and click <strong>Update Now</strong>.</p>\n<p>If you prefer to update manually, you can <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/download/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">download WordPress 4.9.4 here</a>.</p>\n<h2>What&#8217;s new in WordPress 4.9.4?</h2>\n<p>For a complete list of all bug fixes and improvements please see the official <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WordPress 4.9.4 release notes</a>.</p>\n<h2>Learn more about WordPress 4.9</h2>\n<p>WordPress 4.9 brings important improvements and new functions for the Customizer so that you can more easily adjust your site’s design. You can now send a link to share drafts of your changes with your team, publish changes at scheduled times and even lock your changes from editing by other designers.</p>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9944\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-5\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />\n<p>WordPress 4.9 also offers a new gallery widget and an improved text widget that supports images, audio and videos.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"promo-button\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9/\">Learn more about WordPress 4.9</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-4/\">WordPress 4.9.4 Update Available</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-4/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"WordPress 4.9.3 security and maintenance release available\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-3/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-3/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 31 Jan 2018 08:47:24 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"