h as firewalls and filters, even before the updates have been implemented. If you have installed WordPress yourself or use a standard installation from the 1&#38;1 [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-3/\">WordPress 4.9.3 security and maintenance release available</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"jab\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2665:\"<p>WordPress receives additional improvements and bugfixes with <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress 4.9.3</a>.</p>\n<p>As always, <strong>Managed WordPress websites will be updated by 1&amp;1 automatically.</strong> <span id=\"result_box\" class=\"\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"\">In addition, we <span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\">constantly</span> protect your WordPress websites, through technical measures such as firewalls and filters, even before the updates have been implemented.</span></span></p>\n<p>If you have installed WordPress yourself or use a standard installation from the 1&amp;1 App Center, you can update to 4.9.3 from your WordPress <strong>Dashboard.</strong> Select <strong>Updates</strong> and click <strong>Update Now</strong>.</p>\n<p>If you prefer to update manually, you can <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/download/\" target=\"_blank\">download WordPress 4.9.3 here</a>.</p>\n<h2>What&#8217;s new in WordPress 4.9.3?</h2>\n<p>For a complete list of all bug fixes and improvements please see the official <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress 4.9.3 release notes</a>.</p>\n<h2>Learn more about WordPress 4.9</h2>\n<p>WordPress 4.9 brings important improvements and new functions for the Customizer so that you can more easily adjust your site’s design. You can now send a link to share drafts of your changes with your team, publish changes at scheduled times and even lock your changes from editing by other designers.</p>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9944\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-5\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />\n<p>WordPress 4.9 also offers a new gallery widget and an improved text widget that supports images, audio and videos.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"promo-button\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9/\">Learn more about WordPress 4.9</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-3/\">WordPress 4.9.3 security and maintenance release available</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-3/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/mo