dition, we <span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"-1\">constantly</span> protect your WordPress websites, through technical measures such as firewalls and filters, even before the updates have been implemented.</span></span></p>\n<p>If you have installed WordPress yourself or use a standard installation from the 1&amp;1 App Center, you can update to 4.9.1 from your WordPress <strong>Dashboard.</strong> Select <strong>Updates</strong> and click <strong>Update Now</strong>.</p>\n<p>If you prefer to update manually, you can <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/download/\" target=\"_blank\">download WordPress 4.9.1 here</a>.</p>\n<h2>What&#8217;s new in WordPress 4.9.1?</h2>\n<p>For a complete list of all bug fixes and improvements please see the official <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress 4.9.1 release notes</a>.</p>\n<h2>Learn more about WordPress 4.9</h2>\n<p>WordPress 4.9 brings important improvements and new functions for the Customizer so that you can more easily adjust your site’s design. You can now send a link to share drafts of your changes with your team, publish changes at scheduled times and even lock your changes from editing by other designers.</p>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9944\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-5\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />\n<p>WordPress 4.9 also offers a new gallery widget and an improved text widget that supports images, audio and videos.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"promo-button\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9/\">Learn more about WordPress 4.9</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-1/\">WordPress 4.9.1 Update Available</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9-1/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"12\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"WordPress 4.9: What’s New?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 13 Nov 2017 14:15:57 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Information\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"WCMS\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Web Hosting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"featured_wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"highlighted\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"https://community.1and1.com/?p=9938\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:567:\"<p>WordPress 4.9 brings important improvements and new functions for the Customizer so that you can more easily adjust your site&#8217;s design. You can now send a link to share drafts of your changes with your team, publish changes at scheduled times and even lock your changes from editing by other designers. WordPress 4.9 also offers [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9/\">WordPress 4.9: What&#8217;s New?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Philipp Bellmann\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7363:\"<p>WordPress 4.9 brings important improvements and new functions for the Customizer so that you can more easily adjust your site&#8217;s design. You can now send a link to share drafts of your changes with your team, publish changes at scheduled times and even lock your changes from editing by other designers.</p>\n<p>WordPress 4.9 also offers a new gallery widget and an improved text widget that supports images, audio and videos.</p>\n<p>Improved help articles and security notices help you create menus more easily and publish new content or design changes faster and more securely.</p>\n<h2>Widget Updates</h2>\n<h3>The New Gallery Widget</h3>\n<p>Improvements to the media management functions let you add a WordPress gallery as a widget in any widget area you like. Just give it a title, choose the images from your media library and you&#8217;re done!</p>\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9944\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-5\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-5-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />Text Widget: Add Media with a Single Click</h3>\n<p>You can now add images, videos and audio files to a text widget – just click the <strong>Add Media</strong> button in the widget.</p>\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9943\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-4.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-4\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-4.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-4-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-4-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-4-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />Improvements to the Customizer</h2>\n<h3>Schedule Changes: Publish Design Changes at Scheduled Times</h3>\n<p>WordPress 4.9 allows you to save design changes as drafts and publish them at a scheduled time – the same way you do for posts. Simply select the date and time when you want your changes to go live!</p>\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9947\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-8.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-8\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-8.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-8-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-8-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-8-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />Share Your Design Drafts Using a Link</h3>\n<p>If you are working on your website&#8217;s design and want to get feedback from your team or your customer, you can now share a link to your design drafts. This makes your work more efficient and lets you more easily collect and implement feedback!</p>\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9948\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-9.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-9\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-9.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-9-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-9-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-9-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />Protect Your Changes with a Design Lock</h3>\n<p>In situations where more than one designer is working on a website, it&#8217;s possible for designer A to accidentally overwrite changes from designer B. The design lock in WordPress 4.9 lets you protect your design draft so that no one can make changes or delete your work.</p>\n<h2>Improvements for Developers</h2>\n<h3>Syntax Highlighting and Error Checking in the Editor</h3>\n<p>Have you ever had a display problem but simply could not find the error in the CSS you worked so hard to write?</p>\n<p>The new syntax highlighting and error checking functions in the CSS editor and the user-defined HTML widget make it easier to scan your CSS so that you can find code errors faster.</p>\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9945\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-6.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-6\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-6.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-6-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-6-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-6-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />Sandbox and Tips for Greater Security</h3>\n<p>WordPress 4.9 warns you before saving a corrupted code change to a theme or plugin, so you can sleep soundly at night.</p>\n<p>If you edit your themes and plugins directly, for instance without a child theme, WordPress 4.9 also politely warns you that this is a risky practice. Be on the safe side and create a backup of your data before saving, so that the data won&#8217;t be overwritten by the next update.</p>\n<h2>Improvements to Website Layout</h2>\n<h3>Better Help for Creating Menus</h3>\n<p>In the past, working with menus was not always as intuitive as you might have liked. The new version therefore includes clearer instructions and a cleaned-up display to help you create your menus more easily.</p>\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9942\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-3.png\" alt=\"wordpress-4-9-img-3\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1218\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-3.png 2560w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-3-300x143.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-3-768x365.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/wordpress-4-9-img-3-1024x487.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />More Reliable Theme Changes</h3>\n<p>In the past when you changed themes, menus and widgets sometimes got mixed up and changed positions. When you change themes in WordPress 4.9, menus and widgets will more reliably stay in their proper places.</p>\n<p>A preview function also lets you test your widgets and menus with a different theme.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-9/\">WordPress 4.9: What&#8217;s New?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/Comm